<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Jun1938"><font color="red">16 June 1938</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Daniel Brody): My book &mdash; on which I am working all day and all night as well &mdash; is to be published by Faber and Faber (London) and the Viking Press (New York). </div>
